to $50 million in merchandise sales. 
</P>
<P>
	SLOC president Mitt Romney thanked the crowd for showing up --  
and for pitching in their dollars. 
</P>
<P>
	``You're buying things, that helps too,'' Romney said. ``We've  
had a bit of a drought. People were a little nervous.'' 
</P>
