<HEADLINE> Cosby Talks To Colgate Graduates </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	HAMILTON, N.Y. (AP) -- Wearing a maroon baseball cap with a gold  
tassel hanging off to one side, Bill Cosby had some fatherly advice 
for Colgate University graduates. 
</P>
<P>
	``You're out of here. You can't sit around anymore. (Get a)  
J.O.B,'' he said in a commencement speech Sunday before the 677 
graduates. 
</P>
